Introduction

Gong Myung is a South Korean singer and actor under Saram Entertainment. He debuted as a member of the boy group 5URPRISE in November 2014 under Fantagio Entertainment. He is best known for appearing in the dramas "Revolutionary Love", "Bride of the Water God", and "Lovers of the Red Sky".
